title: Archaic Kinds Of Fun
body:
What’s the most impossible job you can think of? For Jo Holbrook, The Tank, Killer Extradonaire…it’s being a bodyguard. Leave it to Fury to kick it up a notch. Now she’s playing chauffeur for Tony Stark and trying to figure out where her life went wrong. At least there’s pancakes.

For The Record

November 1, 2014DARCY“Yo, Skye! You in here?!” Darcy called out as she walked into Tony’s lab. She heard music, and she knew Tony wasn’t playing it because he was out on a date with Pepper…

Read more…

Here comes the next celebrity crush of X💘💖=))))

Spoilerman w British kid accent không thể ấn tượng hơn😂😂 Ngay từ đợt thấy dàn cast của Civil War đã thấy ấn tượng (dù là chưa thích lắm lol) với baby face của Tom huhu mà rõ ràng ẻm hơn mình 2 tuổi cơ mà😃😃 Nhưng phải đến Infinity War mới khiến mình ngộ Tom vô cùng luôn, phải xem lại Homecoming cho đỡ miss cái miệng cóc với cái giọng léo nhéo đấy hic😢😢 =))) Xinh xắn đáng yêu lơ ngơ ngầu lòi gì anh cũng có😘😘😘

When Tony gets back to earth the first thing he will be thinking about is finding Pepper of course. He will...
body:
I had a thought.

When Tony gets back to earth the first thing he will be thinking about is finding Pepper of course. He will hurry home to see if she is okay. What if all he finds is a pile of ash -and a positive pregnancy test.
